{"tid":1434985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[脫離同溫層] 招集跨區公民記者","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:20.000Z","uid":186,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7478a17dd0f3679ac4b0289edabe6c65bf4775e7","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跨區公民記者<br />\nInterdistrict citizen journalists<br />\n</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">Why?</span></span></strong><br />\n我哋相信<br />\n<strong>1. 脫離同溫層，不再圍爐取暖</strong><br />\n我哋會以中立姿態，讓戰友檢討及中立淺藍作理性分析。究竟民意為何物。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 記錄及反映小市民聲音及如何被影響</strong></span><br />\n 製作民宣素材時，受影響小市民往往被主流媒體忽略。衝突畫面往往係最juicy。但小市民如何被衝突畫面影響會係最被忽略，往往在民宣有最大影響力。認真想想衝突時，邊個最影響市民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3. 即時搜證，有系統地及記錄第一手資訊</strong></span><br />\n 十八區街坊有手機就可以即時紀錄或直播，長遠可協助打官司用途及統計分析用途。<br />\n<br />\n我哋想盡量用最真實，最表露無遺的事實報道，因為香港人有知情權，每一香港人都可以清楚明白香港現時發生的事情，亦希望大家參與我們的民間記者，令更多香港人知道所有事情的真相。<br />\n<br />\n有見近日十八區都有不同的社會動盪，我哋想希望收集主流媒體以外的畫面及聲音。一個記者係無可能跑得禁快去唔同區。為此我地希望召集不同的義務民間記者作第一手的採訪及報導。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">How?</span></strong></span><br />\n我哋需要<br />\n一班分佈係十八區唔同既公民記者,經過screening同面見(詳細唔會公佈,以防搞事者知道)。我哋唔係做緊犯法事情，行中立街坊路線，歡迎各位和理非加入。<br />\n<br />\n我哋最需要<ins>有心有時間</ins>，可以on call同唔怕做路人行係街上(法律上我地係可以行街)。<br />\n同時，我哋亦需要一班<ins>文字編輯及設計工作者巴絲打</ins>將一手資料轉化成中立既新聞。<br />\n另外，我地都需要<ins>科技巴絲</ins>利用不同媒體放大市民聲音。同時，會利用收集的資料以<ins>統計人士</ins>作分析。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">What? </span></strong></span><br />\n第一步。招募一大班有志人士，不論年齡男女黃藍。詳細會係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">見面時</span></span>會講，係到講哂埋咩鬼都知。因第一次行動可能好快就需要我地。<br />\n<br />\n資訊會由Tg channel,Facebook,Youtube,Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">Frequent Q and A</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>無記者證點算?</strong><br />\n公民記者，稱民間記者，是指不屬於傳統傳媒體系以外的新聞工作者，雖然公民記者以「記者」為名，但由於自身或所屬團體大多自外於原本的傳媒產業，且不一定擁有新聞相關的專業素養，因此並不完全能融入於傳媒產業的從業人員當中，所以較不容易取得記者證。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>行前面想我地死？</strong><br />\n我哋目標係普通市民於衝突發生時既反應。示威者同警察前線嘅情況有不同嘅主流記者作記錄，但被影響的市民往往卻被忽略。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有危險點算？</strong><br />\n當突發現場發生任何危險情況，希望大家以自身安全為先考慮因素，不鼓吹如其他前線人員般繼續向前進。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點樣先可以加入？</strong><br />\n不論任何學歷，不論任何行業，不論任何年紀。只要你有心，願意付出空閒嘅時間，站在中立/和理非/為市民發聲嘅態度，即可加入我哋。當然，每個崗位所需嘅人數有限，我地會透過每位所填報嘅資料作安排。只要有心，我地需要你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>需要做ｄ咩？</strong><br />\n採訪組：需要落區進行訪問，突發採訪需on call到現場拍攝有關片段及採訪街坊。（可由你地自己選擇）<br />\n後製組：需要將採訪組之材料進行短片合輯，文字編輯及設計。<br />\nPR組：可協助讓更多人去知道我地嘅團隊，或與其他媒體或人仕溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>會唔會有鬼入去做搜證工作?</strong><br />\n我哋目標係普通市民於衝突發生時既反應。示威者同警察前線嘅情況有不同嘅主流記者作記錄。如果佢哋有影到你，請禮貌向佢哋講，我地守則係唔會影示威者同警察大頭，主力Target普通市民於衝突發生時既反應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>加入方法?</strong><br />\n我地團隊會有專人聯絡你做準備<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/QYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FQYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCFuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=15df65c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/QYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，再重申。<br />\n我地團隊並無同其他機構/團體/平台有任何掛鉤。<br />\n希望大家可以踴躍參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4nnFPZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4nnFPZ.png&h=32151fba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74025337e0e4dc186bcbf0b9361c68d6b74c6c28","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"暫時公海:<br />\ntg: <a href=\"http://t.me/interdistrict18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterdistrict18&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCFuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=2f63d605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/interdistrict18</a>"},{"pid":"0e53340b5e75df7a530a0382cef82a7ec0755f37","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a382db711ac31336724d034ab394de0ac5bf341","tid":1434985,"uid":176303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"其實越來越多事件令我們相信目前在前線的很多警務人員都是來自內地:<br />\n(1) 他們未能出示委任證<br />\n(2）他們不熟悉香港法例，隨便入私人地方，男警搜女人身，這都不是香港警察慣常的做法<br />\n(3）他們不熟悉議員名字，從他們的反應看到，他們並非故意扮作不認識<br />\n(4）外國記者報道，已經有數萬操廣東話警員從大陸到了香港<br />\n(5）有片段影到警員用普通話向彼此稱呼為「同志們」"},{"pid":"0f9fa1c9701e8c26ad19b79fb2e4ce009a2bbb47","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"招集有志脫離同溫層巴絲"},{"pid":"c388d901b3503c2c90be699146eb5dd2a964c212","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"為戰友脫離同溫層"},{"pid":"7e813a5668a05d394cc66207905e75838c2d238a","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"已加入嘅巴絲 我地有人遂一聯絡"},{"pid":"8773d1fedbf26e2f56588f9b52154a1c67ee4719","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e813a5668a05d394cc66207905e75838c2d238a","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"已加入嘅巴絲 我地有人遂一聯絡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"麻煩耐心等待"},{"pid":"8a428dd4580eada59a11e4730a5ddf012a7a2b03","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b5b95ef8ead5bd835f590f740d2e3e03b5bda7","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15febefd25b80195ea79d75c28a8861dd543e615","tid":1434985,"uid":274589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"是否真正中立？<br />\n如果市民受示威人士影響，都會寫？"},{"pid":"05ba5814d9478a994e90d0d8253b46fecb3e4102","tid":1434985,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"8.9       機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日1:00 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGQPZ5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGQPZ5c.png&h=7a7f7945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"320d7260dcb651d93b55a7694e4ed96af83c1de5","tid":1434985,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:38:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0da5a58cbc99a1a71bebef2298de58f2cc58e3c","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949346bfdb66251a3f0253fda4aec2e8a07cf950","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa734f680cfb58fc69e7f7e4cacbd624b54f23d","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202ced28b67d6557a98bae8f243c462377e5dbfe","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b81e91d12ea19d9f0b4b171ec7d55200a0a232c","tid":1434985,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"761525b9e25bb68328d5dbaf4cd64c914204e82d","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cb650ef2a971c65a3dfc1a259c6c98e139a64a","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"242fd5c832bcc224afb63c48425b8a90ea5321c6","tid":1434985,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"個idea幾好，你地班底有咩人?"},{"pid":"e8fbd1c2e86d0a7d3c2a796884d2c74862b6c91f","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242fd5c832bcc224afb63c48425b8a90ea5321c6","tid":1434985,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"個idea幾好，你地班底有咩人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"都係一班巴絲<br />\n同唔同專業人士"},{"pid":"7f841fd8fb6c7da4a7736f67864bffd3a9121cae","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fbd1c2e86d0a7d3c2a796884d2c74862b6c91f","tid":1434985,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242fd5c832bcc224afb63c48425b8a90ea5321c6","tid":1434985,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"個idea幾好，你地班底有咩人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"都係一班巴絲<br />\n同唔同專業人士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"入group先詳講 <br />\n呢到公海"},{"pid":"c801fac02bf83cc8e0bf386efcf1671631d33c2c","tid":1434985,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"咁樣會唔會比人入話扮記者？"},{"pid":"49ccf51ff58157c3d7e033b74dc05437e651426f","tid":1434985,"uid":69276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}